<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.7">
<l>kuruntamoṉṟocit tāṉoṭuñceṉṟu kūṭiyāṭivi ḻācceytu</l>
<l>tiruntunāṉmaṟai yōrirāppaka lēttivāḻtiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>karuntaṭamukil vaṇṇaṉaikkaṭaik koṇṭukaitoḻum pattarka</l>
<l>ḷiruntavūrili rukkumāṉiṭa rettavaṅkaḷcey tārkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirukkōṭṭiyūr dwell those of the four perfect vedas,</l>
<l>praising day and night, celebrating the festivals</l>
<l>and going, joining, [and] dancing</l>
<l rend="indent">with him who broke the wild lime tree.</l>
<l>What penance has been performed</l>
<l>by the people who inhabit this city</l>
<l rend="indent">where devotees join [their] hands in worship</l>
<l rend="indent">to him with the hue of a broad, dark cloud?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
